## Implementation Architecture

### File Structure

**Core Logic**:
- [app.js](file:///Users/cwb/.gemini/antigravity/playground/inner-juno/app.js): Classification and scoring functions
- [strategic-insights.js](file:///Users/cwb/.gemini/antigravity/playground/inner-juno/strategic-insights.js): Insights rendering module
- [index.html](file:///Users/cwb/.gemini/antigravity/playground/inner-juno/index.html): UI components

**Data Flow**:
1. Videos loaded from [data.js](file:///Users/cwb/.gemini/antigravity/playground/inner-juno/data.js)
2. [processDataByVideo()](file:///Users/cwb/.gemini/antigravity/playground/inner-juno/app.js#146-237) computes archetypes and quality scores
3. [analyzeFormatPerformance()](file:///Users/cwb/.gemini/antigravity/playground/inner-juno/strategic-insights.js#4-49) groups videos by archetype
4. `identifyOpportunities()` detects actionable patterns
5. [updateStrategicInsights()](file:///Users/cwb/.gemini/antigravity/playground/inner-juno/strategic-insights.js#303-315) renders insights on filter/selection changes

---

## Audit Report Alignment

The implementation directly addresses findings from the performance audit:

| Audit Finding | Dashboard Solution |
|---|---|
| **42% retention on Explainers vs 11% on Documentaries** | Format Performance cards instantly show this gap |
| **"September Surge" from topical clustering** | Next phase: Cluster detection algorithm |
| **CTR below 4-6% benchmark** | Packaging Opportunities alert highlights low-CTR videos |
| **67% revenue from top 3 videos** | Next phase: Revenue concentration risk gauge |
| **Duration paradox (5-min outperformed 60-min)** | Format analysis shows performance by video length |

